  "detailed_description": "<h1>XDesktopSoft COLLECTION</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Software</h1>Any problem please  post a thread or send an email<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About XWidget</h2>XWidget is a powerful desktop widget customization engine. It's light, handy with smooth animations. <br>Built-in powerful visual widget editor and widgets online gallery. You can download ALL widgets (more then 1600+) from the built-in gallery with just one-click. <br>Included widgets: Analog/Digital clocks, Calendar, Weather/Forecast, Dock, Launcher, system info/meters (Hard Disk Drive(s), CPU, RAM, Battery), Shortcuts, PhotoAlbum,Notes, Volume, Net monitor, Email, RSS feed, Animated/swim on screen elements, Music Player, Spectrum Visualization and more...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Personalize your desktop and bring your desktop alive with widgets.<br></li><li>Create your own widgets or suites easily with the built-in xwidget designer (APIs/cores, javascript coding)<br></li><li>Use the build-in online gallery and download ALL widgets (more than 1600+) with just one-click.<br></li><li>Wide variety of widgets separated in categories DateTime, Weather, System, Information, Media and Others.<br></li><li>XWidget can be used in parallel to any other Steam game or application.<br></li><li>Support Steam Cloud Sync Widgets and UserData.<br></li><li>Minimum CPU and RAM usage.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Performance</strong></h2>XWidget aims to deliver an entertaining experience while using as few system resources as possible. Various options to tweak quality and performance exist to make XWidget suit your needs.",
  "about_the_game": "Any problem please  post a thread or send an email<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About XWidget</h2>XWidget is a powerful desktop widget customization engine. It's light, handy with smooth animations. <br>Built-in powerful visual widget editor and widgets online gallery. You can download ALL widgets (more then 1600+) from the built-in gallery with just one-click. <br>Included widgets: Analog/Digital clocks, Calendar, Weather/Forecast, Dock, Launcher, system info/meters (Hard Disk Drive(s), CPU, RAM, Battery), Shortcuts, PhotoAlbum,Notes, Volume, Net monitor, Email, RSS feed, Animated/swim on screen elements, Music Player, Spectrum Visualization and more...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Personalize your desktop and bring your desktop alive with widgets.<br></li><li>Create your own widgets or suites easily with the built-in xwidget designer (APIs/cores, javascript coding)<br></li><li>Use the build-in online gallery and download ALL widgets (more than 1600+) with just one-click.<br></li><li>Wide variety of widgets separated in categories DateTime, Weather, System, Information, Media and Others.<br></li><li>XWidget can be used in parallel to any other Steam game or application.<br></li><li>Support Steam Cloud Sync Widgets and UserData.<br></li><li>Minimum CPU and RAM usage.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Performance</strong></h2>XWidget aims to deliver an entertaining experience while using as few system resources as possible. Various options to tweak quality and performance exist to make XWidget suit your needs.",
